  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.ebi.ac.uk/swo/SWO_0000150">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty"/>
    <rdfs:comment>This property, together with 'uses software', is probably best modelled as a child of has_part. Its current position in the property hierarchy is based on simplicity of use. 'uses platform' was deemed an appropriate addition (rather than making use of already extant has_part or 'uses software') due to the already present definitions of those classes which restrict their use to particular situations.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">uses platform</rdfs:label>
  </rdf:Description>
